nodes.text: A dojo was located in Galactic City on the planet Coruscant during the reign of the Galactic Empire. As part of an investigation undertaken by Colonel Wullf Yularen, Captain Thrawn, Ensign Eli Vanto, and Officers Brook and Roenton, into dojos located in the Federal District that trained government employees connected to powerful senators and other political figures. They traveled to this dojo in order to gain information into who Nightswan was and what their motivations were prior to arriving at the Yinchom Dojo.
